{"tid":1185992,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019居屋]對唔住，我係on9仔，求各位大佬指點下","createTime":"2019-06-04T15:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T01:21:40.000Z","uid":138834,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5d602152136a85916469ed2404e926b01f266e","tid":1185992,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我知自己衰on9，依家好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n份白表我唔小心重複交左<br />\n我網上交表<br />\n第一次交時，master card要send個OTP密碼俾我，但第一次我完左倒數都未收到<br />\n<br />\n完左倒數之後Master話我付款失敗<br />\n<br />\n咁我就填第二次，第二次成功俾錢<br />\n<br />\n但頭先睇返email，有兩封居屋申請確認<br />\n信用卡戶口都扣左兩次錢<br />\n<br />\n依家好撚心急<br />\n請問咁樣係唔係冇得救<br />\n<br />\n我見佢2018有份表係撤回申請，但2019就冇<br />\n諗住聽日打上去問有冇得撤回第一份申請<br />\n<br />\n一陣抽又冇得抽，政府仲要食鳩我500蚊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e62bfe37c8185de747c4cc50f804b39193720d","tid":1185992,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"彩你都有味"},{"pid":"2919bd47859df80763421672a46e0ef29bb300c7","tid":1185992,"uid":8528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"冇㗎啦！"},{"pid":"0173a753ec01ecbb9a7b14c3c96b7960e5173abb","tid":1185992,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"等下round啦師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66654e5007b8e